Emit structured document metadata as JSON (title, author, creator, producer, creation/modification dates, page count, and extended properties)

Usage: udoc metadata [OPTIONS] <FILE>

Arguments:
  <FILE>  Input document

Options:
  -o, --output <FILE>    Write the report here instead of stdout
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format: `json` (default) or `text` [default: json]
  -h, --help             Print help
